WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.199 --> 00:00:08.880
Hi, and welcome to your CCC intake. This
tool is here to help you with the

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:14.000
re-entry process. It will ask you about
your life, your goals, and what you need

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:18.960
to be successful. The answers you give
will help create a personal plan just

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:23.519
for you. This program will also make a
summary for your case manager, your

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:28.080
parole officer, and other staff at the
center so they can understand your needs

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:32.960
and support you better. So, how does
this tool work? When you click start

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:37.760
intake below, you'll start a
conversation with a chatbot computer

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:43.840
program. The chatbot will ask you about
where you plan to live, your job

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:48.640
history, your education, and more. After
each question, you'll have time to type

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:52.719
your answer. Feel free to be as open as
you're comfortable with. The more

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:57.840
information you give, the more the tool
can help you build a great plan.

00:00:55.520 --> 00:01:03.039
Take your time with the questions. You
can stop and think as much as you need

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:07.280
to. The whole thing takes about 30 to 60
minutes, but if you need to leave and

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:12.640
come back later, it will remember where
you left off. When you're done, the tool

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:17.759
will use your answers to create an
action plan just for you. This plan

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:22.320
gives you and your case manager ideas
for reaching your goals and can make

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:26.880
suggestions for getting jobs, housing,
and other services. You and your case

00:01:25.119 --> 00:01:31.759
manager will sit down and review the
plan together.

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:36.079
Two notes before getting started.
First, it's important to note that you

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:42.079
are chatting with a computer, not a real
person. This is called artificial

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:46.880
intelligence or AI. Also, please note
that your case manager and other CCC

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:51.040
support staff, as well as any future
officer you're assigned to, will be able

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:59.040
to see the answers you give during this
intake. That's it. Thanks for listening.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:59.040
Click start intake to get started.

